{"arkId":"cl010099963","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099963","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1640","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1640,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"2e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Jolly, Josias","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1642","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8428","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond du bo\u00eetier orn\u00e9 d\u0027une peinture \u00e9maill\u00e9e repr\u00e9sentant La Vierge et l\u0027Enfant en compagnie de saint Jean-Baptiste et de sainte Elisabeth d\u0027apr\u00e8s une gravure de Petrus II de Jode d\u0027apr\u00e8s Erasmus II Quelin, la sc\u00e8ne se d\u00e9roulant pr\u00e8s d\u0027une balustrade au-dessus de laquelle est relev\u00e9 un rideau rouge. Contre-\u00e9mail repr\u00e9sentant La Visitation sur un fond de paysage. Ext\u00e9rieur du couvercle \u00e9maill\u00e9 d\u0027une Vierge \u00e0 l\u0027Enfant d\u0027apr\u00e8s Simon Vouet : la m\u00e8re et l\u0027enfant se regardent avec tendresse. L\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle d\u00e9cor\u00e9 du Mariage de la Vierge. Charni\u00e8re au-dessus du XII ; t\u00eate du pendant en forme d\u0027anneau bomb\u00e9. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, au centre, sur fond de paysage se trouve une figure de femme, bras crois\u00e9s sur la poitrine (l\u0027Esp\u00e9rance ?). Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre et d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec cordelette rouge. Cliquet reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de fleurs de fraisier comme le coq ovale \u00e0 un pied. Quatre piliers ayant la forme de balustres.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Jolly AParis","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,8","displayDimension":"7,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,8","displayDimension":"5,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1,8","displayDimension":"1,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 640 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935 ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e des Arts d\u00e9coratifs le 4 novembre 1935 ; retour au mus\u00e9e du Louvre, arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1982.","jabachInv